From: 1:3' 
To: IIM Reynolds 
Subject: meeting tomorrow 
Date: The, 13 Jul 2021 19:46:59 +0000 
Attachments: 
2021.07.13_Court_Subpoena_-adf 
M, 
Looking forward to meeting with you and at your office tomorrow at 9:30am. As we've previously discussed, 
I'm attaching a trial subpoena requiring to testify at our trial, which is scheduled to begin on November 29, 
2021. I expect we will call to testify sometime in early December 2021 during that trial. 
After our prep tomorrow, I do not think we will need to meet with again until we get closer to trial. I'll plan to 
reach back out in early November to arrange for a VTC on which we can conduct a refresher prep session and to arrange 
for travel and hotel for trial. 
Thanks and see you tomorrow. 
Best, 
Assistant United States Attorney 
Southern District of New York 
1 St. Andrew% Plaza 
New York, NY 10007 
EFTA00019869
